at would be great*<br> <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ueqtrader420.showPublicProfile?language=EN>EqTrader420</A> at: 4/8/02 9:33:26 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#403C50><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ukulanaesoulsease.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kulanae Soulsease</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Guardian of Underfoot</span><br>  Posts: 889<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(4/9/02 1:12:07 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilisbrellserilisdiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11331.topic&index=1>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> <BR><img src=http://web1.noment.com/dsummers//EQ/Kulanae6.gif height=158 width=119></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_question_mark.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Bard Solo Question</span><hr size=1> Before I offer advice answer me this.....what is your defense at right now? <p><font size=2 face="Tempus Sans ITC, Verdana, Helvetica"><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=8687>Kulanae Soulsease</a></font><br><font size=2 face="Helvetica">Virtuoso of <a href=http://www.watchers-brell.com>Watchers</a><br><br><i>Joy is in the ears that hear!</i></font></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#464446><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/usalmindria.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Salmindria</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Adventurer of Underfoot</span><br>  Posts: 3<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(4/9/02 1:32:41 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilisbrellser